what could have happened.

348
00:25:14.981 --> 00:25:17.584
You just don't belong
in my world, Bella.

349
00:25:22.655 --> 00:25:24.156
I belong with you.

350
00:25:26.092 --> 00:25:28.227
No. You don't.

351
00:25:30.930 --> 00:25:32.198
