488
00:37:42.060 --> 00:37:43.595
Dude, come on.

489
00:37:43.629 --> 00:37:44.763
CHET: Come here for a sec!

490
00:37:48.867 --> 00:37:51.770
I think I know those guys.

491
00:37:51.803 --> 00:37:54.606
CHET: We got beer!
We got bikes!

492
00:37:54.640 --> 00:37:56.942
Well, they seem great.
