500
00:38:35.647 --> 00:38:37.583
I'm sorry, I thought
you were somebody else.

501
00:38:37.616 --> 00:38:39.785
No, that's cool. I'll be whoever
you want me to be, honey.

502
00:38:39.818 --> 00:38:42.087
