503
00:38:47.058 --> 00:38:49.060
You promised me,
nothing reckless.

504
00:38:50.128 --> 00:38:51.497
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

505
00:38:53.765 --> 00:38:55.801
You promised it would be
as if you never existed.

506
00:38:56.868 --> 00:38:57.803
(CLEARS THROAT)

507
00:39:02.107 --> 00:39:03.509
